# Object Property: pmdco:PMD_0001028 (in response to)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0001028 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0001028 "PERSON: Joerg Waitelonis")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0001028 "als Antwort auf"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0001028 "in response to"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0001028 "Umkehrung von antwortet mit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0001028 "inverse of responds with"@en)
InverseObjectProperties(pmdco:PMD_0001028 pmdco:PMD_0001029)

# Object Property: pmdco:PMD_0001029 (responds with)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0001029 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0001029 "PERSON: Joerg Waitelonis")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0001029 "antwortet mit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0001029 "responds with"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0001029 "Die realisierbare Entität muss durch einen Reiz „stimuliert“ werden, um mit der Reaktion zu reagieren. Der Träger der realisierbaren Entität muss sowohl an der Stimulation als auch an der Reaktion teilnehmen."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0001029 "The realizable entity must be \"stimulated\" by some Stimulus in order to respond with the Response. The bearer of the realizable entity must participate in Stimulation as well as in Response."@en)
ObjectPropertyDomain(pmdco:PMD_0001029 obo:BFO_0000017)

# Object Property: pmdco:PMD_0020020 (interacts with)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0020020 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0020020 "PERSON: Philipp von Hartrott")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0020020 "interacts with"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0020020 "interagiert mit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0020020 "A relation between participants of a process indicating that some of the participants SDCs are affected during the process due to the interaction of the participants."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0020020 "Eine Beziehung zwischen Teilnehmern eines Prozesses, die darauf hinweist, dass einige SDCs der Teilnehmer während des Prozesses aufgrund der Interaktion der Teilnehmer betroffen sind."@de)
SymmetricObjectProperty(pmdco:PMD_0020020)
ObjectPropertyDomain(pmdco:PMD_0020020 obo:BFO_0000040)
ObjectPropertyRange(pmdco:PMD_0020020 obo:BFO_0000040)

# Object Property: pmdco:PMD_0025013 (changes quality)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025013 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025013 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025013 "changes quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025013 "verändert die Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025013 "indicates that a process changes a quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025013 "zeigt an, dass ein Prozess eine Qualität verändert"@de)
ObjectPropertyDomain(pmdco:PMD_0025013 obo:BFO_0000015)
ObjectPropertyRange(pmdco:PMD_0025013 obo:BFO_0000019)

# Object Property: pmdco:PMD_0025998 (hat relationale Qualität)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025998 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025998 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025998 "has relational quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025998 "hat relationale Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025998 "a relation between an independent continuant (the bearer) and a relational quality, in which the quality specifically depends on the bearer for its existence"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025998 "eine Beziehung zwischen einem unabhängigen Kontinuum (dem Träger) und einer relationalen Qualität, bei der die Qualität in ihrer Existenz speziell vom Träger abhängt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0025998 "material has relational quality mass proportion m, and portion of iron has the same relational quality mass proportion m"@en)
InverseObjectProperties(pmdco:PMD_0025998 pmdco:PMD_0025999)
ObjectPropertyDomain(pmdco:PMD_0025998 obo:BFO_0000004)
ObjectPropertyRange(pmdco:PMD_0025998 obo:BFO_0000145)

# Object Property: pmdco:PMD_0025999 (relational quality of)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025999 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0025999 "The 'relational quality of' is more strict that 'quality of' from RO, since domain is 'relational quality'. The motivtion to introduce an object property for relational qualities is the following:
RO's 'quality of' is functional i.e., a->b, a->c => b=c. The functionality is relevant for most of the SDC -> IC triples, expect for relational qualities, which per definiton can be simultaneously inherited in >=2 ICs. Thus,  'relational quality of'  has the same intention to connect SDC to IC, however, without cardinality constraints."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025999 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025999 "relational quality of"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025999 "relationale Qualität von"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025999 "a relation between a relational quality and an independent continuant (the bearer), in which the quality specifically depends on the bearer for its existence"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025999 "eine Beziehung zwischen einer relationalen Qualität und einem unabhängigen Kontinuum (dem Träger), bei der die Existenz der Qualität speziell vom Träger abhängt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0025999 "mass proportion m is relational qualitiy of material, and the same mass proportion m is relational qualitiy of portion of iron"@en)



