# Class: pmdco:PMD_0000506 (akustische Eigenschaft)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0000506 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0000506 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'acoustic capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0000506 "PERSON: Joerg Waitelonis")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0000506 "acoustic property"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0000506 "akustische Eigenschaft"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0000506 "An acoustic property is a material property representing characteristics of a material that determine its interaction with sound waves, such as absorption, reflection, and transmission."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0000506 "Eine akustische Eigenschaft ist eine Materialeigenschaft, die Eigenschaften eines Materials darstellt, die seine Wechselwirkung mit Schallwellen bestimmen, wie z. B. Absorption, Reflexion und Transmission."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0000506 "A piezoelectric transducer has the acoustic capability to emit ultrasound at frequencies up to 10 MHz"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0000506 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0000506 obo:BFO_0000020)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0000506 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:BFO_0000054 pmdco:PMD_0000517))

