# Class: pmdco:PMD_0020268 (characteristic value)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0020268 "characteristic value"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:comment pmdco:PMD_0020268 "it is difficult to axiomatically assert this class based on being output of a measurement procedure because the disjoint complement class \"fundamental physical property\" can also be measured.

Characteristic values may serve as (quantitative) comparison criteria."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0020268 "a property that can only be determined through a specific possibly standardized measurement or testing procedure."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0020268 "Brinell hardness"@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0020268 obo:BFO_0000020)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0020268 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:IAO_0000417 obo:IAO_0000109))

