# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025001 (Zusammensetzung)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025001 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0025001 "There's a dfference between composition and chemical compositon for the following reason: chemical compositon is relevant when the mass/volume/mole proportions of chemical elements(!) are identified, whlist composition includes proportions of molecules, other pure chemical substances, or even proptions of objects (in an object aggregate)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025001 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025001 "Zusammensetzung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025001 "composition"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025001 "Composition is an intensive quality which defines types and proportions of compounds present in a material entity and is subject of some composition data item."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025001 "Zusammensetzung ist eine intensive Qualität, die Arten und Anteile von Verbindungen definiert, die in einer materiellen Einheit vorhanden sind, und Gegenstand einiger Zusammensetzungsdatenelemente ist."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0025001 "4 vol.% nitric acid solution, Styrene-Butadiene-Styrene (SBS) Block Copolymer with 50 vol.% of both styrene and butadiene"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0025001 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000064 pmdco:PMD_0025001 "Composition is a collective property of a portion of matter, i.e., the triple portion of matter has quality composition holds. As \"has quality\" is an inverse  functional property, only one instance of portion of matter can have this specific composition. However, proportions describe the relation between the prortion of matter (the whole) and some compound (the part). Thus, the following triples hold: portion of matter has relational quality proportion; portion of matter has part some substance (or whatever is your part); substance has relational quality proportion. \"Has relational quality\" is not inverse functional, i.e., it can point to a single object from 2 distinct subjects."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025001 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025002 (chemical composition data item)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025002 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025002 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025002 "Datenelement zur chemischen Zusammensetzung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025002 "chemical composition data item"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0025002 "chemical composition specification"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025002 "Bei einem Datenelement zur chemischen Zusammensetzung handelt es sich um eine Informationsinhaltseinheit, die sich auf die Zusammensetzung eines Stoffteils bezieht. Es verfügt über Bruchwertspezifikationen für Mitglieder, die Werte für Anteile von Anteilen (reiner) chemischer Elemente angeben, die Teile des Anteils der Materie sind."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025002 "Chemical composition data item is an information content entity that is about composition of a portion of matter. It has members fraction value specifications which specifiy values of propotions of portions of (pure) chemical elements, which are parts of the portion of matter."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0025002 "Steel has quality chemical composition , and the chemical composition data item is about the chemical composition .The chemical composition data item has members fraction specifications of iron and carbon. These fraction specifications specify value of portion of iron and portion of carbon respectively. Furthermore, these fraction specifications specify  values of relational qualities (mass) proportion of iron and (mass) proportion of carbon."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0025002 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025002 pmdco:PMD_0020004)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025002 ObjectIntersectionOf(pmdco:PMD_0020004 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:IAO_0000136 pmdco:PMD_0000551) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:RO_0002351 pmdco:PMD_0025997)))

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025003 (metallic grain structure)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025003 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025003 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment pmdco:PMD_0025003 "ferrite, austenite, martensite, etc."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025003 "metallic grain structure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025003 "metallische Kornstruktur"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025003 "intensive Qualität, die die unterschiedlichen Phasen in der mikroskopischen Struktur eines metallischen Materials verkörpert."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025003 "intensive quality epitomizing the distinct phases in the microscopic structure of a metallic material."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0025003 "false"^^xsd:boolean)
EquivalentClasses(pmdco:PMD_0025003 ObjectExactCardinality(1 pmdco:PMD_0000077 pmdco:PMD_0020023))
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025003 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025009 (materieller Reaktionsprozess)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025009 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025009 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment pmdco:PMD_0025009 "material reacting process has always energy minimization as a driving force."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025009 "material reacting process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025009 "materieller Reaktionsprozess"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025009 "Ein materieller Reaktionsprozess ist ein Prozess, der in einem Teil der Materie aufgrund einiger seiner Dispositionen oder Verhaltenseigenschaften stattfindet, die in einem stimulierenden Prozess umgesetzt werden. Sowohl der materielle Reaktionsprozess als auch der stimulierende Prozess müssen stattfindende Teile eines geplanten Prozesses sein, wenn der geplante Prozess stattfindet."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025009 "Material reacting process is a process which occurs in a portion of matter due to some of its disposition or behavioral material property which has realization in some  stimulating process. Both the material reacting process and stimulating process must be occurent parts of a planned process, if the planned process takes place."@en)
EquivalentClasses(pmdco:PMD_0025009 ObjectIntersectionOf(obo:BFO_0000015 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:BFO_0000066 pmdco:PMD_0000001) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pmdco:PMD_0001028 ObjectIntersectionOf(ObjectUnionOf(obo:BFO_0000016 pmdco:PMD_0000005) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:BFO_0000054 pmdco:PMD_0000950)))))
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025009 obo:BFO_0000015)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025010 (heating)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025010 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025010 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025010 "Heizung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025010 "heating"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025010 "Erwärmung ist eine Temperaturänderung, die dem Temperaturanstieg im System oder Objekt entspricht."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025010 "Heating is a change of temperature which corresponds to the increase of temperature in the system or object."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025010 pmdco:PMD_0000549)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025011 (cooling)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025011 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025011 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025011 "Kühlung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025011 "cooling"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025011 "Cooling is a change of temperature which corresponds to the decrease of temperature in the system or object."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025011 "Kühlung ist eine Temperaturänderung, die einem Temperaturabfall im System oder Objekt entspricht."@de)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025011 pmdco:PMD_0000549)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025016 (Innendurchmesser)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025016 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025016 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025016 "Innendurchmesser"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025016 "inner diameter"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025016 "Der Innendurchmesser ist die Länge einer geraden Linie von einer Innenfläche eines Objekts oder Raums zur anderen Seite seiner Innenfläche durch den Mittelpunkt eines Objekts oder Raums, wenn es eine Innen- und Außenfläche hat."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025016 "Inner diameter is a length of a straight line from one inner surface of an object or space to the other side of its inner surface through the center of an object or space when it has the inside and outside surface."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025016 pmdco:PMD_0050051)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025017 (outer diameter)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025017 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025017 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025017 "Außendurchmesser"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025017 "outer diameter"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025017 "Der Außendurchmesser ist die Länge einer geraden Linie von einer Außenfläche eines Objekts oder Raums zur anderen Seite seiner Außenfläche durch den Mittelpunkt eines Objekts oder Raums, wenn es eine Innen- und Außenfläche hat."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025017 "Outer diameter is a length of a straight line from one outer surface of an object or space to the other side of its outer surface through the center of an object or space when it has the inside and outside surface."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025017 pmdco:PMD_0050051)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025018 (geometric relational quality)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025018 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025018 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025018 "geometric relational quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025018 "geometrische relationale Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025018 "Geometric relational quality is a relational quality describing the geometric relation between two or more independent continuants."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025018 "Geometrische Beziehungsqualität ist eine Beziehungsqualität, die die geometrische Beziehung zwischen zwei oder mehr unabhängigen Kontinuen beschreibt."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0025018 "Elongation of a specimen after a tensile step, i.e., the specimen before and after the test. Angle between a rolling direction of a rolled material and the longitudinal side of a specimen."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0025018 obo:BFO_0000145)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0025997 (Angabe des Bruchwerts)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0025997 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0025997 "PERSON: Kamilla Zaripova")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025997 "Angabe des Bruchwerts"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0025997 "fraction value specification"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025997 "Bei der Bruchwertspezifikation handelt es sich um eine Wertspezifikation, die Informationen über den quantitativen Anteil eines Teils im Verhältnis zu einem angegebenen Ganzen enthält."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0025997 "Fraction value specification is a value specification that contains information about quantitative share of a part relative to a specified whole."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0025997 "2.05 wt.% of carbon in steel, 4 vol.% of nitric acid in a solution"@en)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0040001 (Länge)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0040001 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0040001 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'length' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'DimensionQuality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0000122."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0040001 "PERSON: Lars Vogt")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0040001 obo:PATO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment pmdco:PMD_0040001 "Length is a size that describes the spatial extent of its bearer in one dimension."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0040001 "Länge"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0040001 "length"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0040001 "dimension"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0040001 "Die Länge ist eine eindimensionale Größe."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0040001 "Length is a one dimensional size."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0040001 "A steel rod measures 250 mm in length between its two end faces"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0040001 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0040001 pmdco:PMD_0020132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050000 (Bindung)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050000 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050000 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050000 "Bindung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050000 "bond"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050000 "A bond is a relational quality describing the force interaction between atoms."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050000 "Eine Bindung ist eine relationale Qualität, die die Kraftwechselwirkung zwischen Atomen beschreibt."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0050000 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050000 obo:BFO_0000145)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050001 (covalent bond)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050001 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050001 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0050001 <https://sciencenotes.org/types-of-chemical-bonds/>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050001 "covalent bond"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050001 "kovalente Bindung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050001 "A covalent bond is a bond that forms when nonmetal atoms share electrons to achieve a stable electron configuration."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050001 "Eine kovalente Bindung ist eine Bindung, die entsteht, wenn Nichtmetallatome Elektronen teilen, um eine stabile Elektronenkonfiguration zu erreichen."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0050001 "In a water molecule (H₂O), the hydrogen and oxygen atoms share electrons."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0050001 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050001 pmdco:PMD_0050000)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050002 (metallic bond)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050002 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050002 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0050002 <https://www.thoughtco.com/metallic-bond-definition-properties-and-examples-4117948>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050002 "metallic bond"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050002 "metallische Bindung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050002 "A metallic bond is a bond that forms between metal atoms, where electrons are shared in a \"sea\" of electrons that move freely around the metal ions. This type of bonding gives metals their characteristic properties such as conductivity and malleability."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050002 "Eine Metallbindung ist eine Bindung, die zwischen Metallatomen entsteht, wobei Elektronen in einem „Meer“ von Elektronen geteilt werden, die sich frei um die Metallionen bewegen. Diese Art der Bindung verleiht Metallen ihre charakteristischen Eigenschaften wie Leitfähigkeit und Formbarkeit."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0050002 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050002 pmdco:PMD_0050000)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050003 (Ionenbindung)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050003 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050003 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0050003 <https://sciencenotes.org/types-of-chemical-bonds/>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050003 "Ionenbindung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050003 "ionic bond"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050003 "An ionic bond is a bond that occurs when one atom donates an electron to another atom, resulting in oppositely charged ions that attract each other."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050003 "Eine Ionenbindung ist eine Bindung, die entsteht, wenn ein Atom ein Elektron an ein anderes Atom abgibt, wodurch entgegengesetzt geladene Ionen entstehen, die sich gegenseitig anziehen."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0050003 "An example is the interaction between the atoms of sodium chloride (NaCl), where the sodium atom donates an electron to a chlorine atom."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0050003 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050003 pmdco:PMD_0050000)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050051 (Durchmesser)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050051 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050051 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0050051 "“Diameter.” Merriam-Webster.com Dictionary, Merriam-Webster, https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/diameter. Accessed 5 Dec. 2022.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050051 "Durchmesser"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050051 "diameter"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:seeAlso pmdco:PMD_0050051 <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/2.0.8/Diameter>)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050051 "Die Länge einer geraden Linie durch den Mittelpunkt eines Objekts oder Raums."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050051 "The length of a straight line through the center of an object or space."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050051 pmdco:PMD_0040001)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050153 (thickness)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050153 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050153 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050153 "Dicke"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050153 "thickness"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050153 "A length that describes the measured dimension in one direction of a test piece."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050153 "Diese Klasse beschreibt das gemessene Maß in einer Richtung eines Prüfkörpers."@de)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050153 pmdco:PMD_0040001)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050154 (Breite)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050154 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050154 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050154 "Breite"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050154 "width"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:seeAlso pmdco:PMD_0050154 <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/2.0.8/Width>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:seeAlso pmdco:PMD_0050154 <https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/width>)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050154 "Diese Klasse beschreibt eine horizontale Messung eines Objekts, die im rechten Winkel zur Länge des Objekts vorgenommen wird."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050154 "This class describes a horizontal measurement of an object taken at right angles to the length of the object."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050154 pmdco:PMD_0040001)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050155 (shape)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050155 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050155 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0050155 "“Shape.” Merriam-Webster.com Dictionary, Merriam-Webster, https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/shape. Accessed 13 Jan. 2023.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050155 "Form"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050155 "shape"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050155 "Das sichtbare Ausstattungsmerkmal (räumliche Form oder Kontur) eines bestimmten Objektes oder einer Art von Objekt."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050155 "Extemsive quality, the visible makeup characteristic (spatial form or contour) of a particular item or kind of item."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050155 pmdco:PMD_0020132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050156 (Geometrische Form)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050156 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050156 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0050156 "DIN EN ISO 6892-1:2019")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050156 "Geometrische Form"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050156 "geometry shape"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050156 "Dieses Konzept beschreibt die geometrischen Abmessungen und das Erscheinungsbild (Form und Abmaße) einer Probe, eines Prüfkörpers oder eines Prüfstücks, wie sie üblicherweise durch eine entsprechende Norm definiert sind. Dementsprechend ist der angegebene Formwert in Übereinstimmung mit der definierenden Norm anzugeben, z. B. \"Zugprüfstück Form 1 gemäß Anhang B der Zugversuchsnorm\"."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050156 "This concept describes the geometric dimensions and appearance (shape and dimensions) of a sample, specimen, or test piece as usually defined by a corresponding standard. Accordingly, the shape value given is in accordance with the defining standard, e.g., ‘tensile test piece shape 1 in accordance with annex B of the tensile test standard’."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050156 pmdco:PMD_0050155)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0050157 (3D Geometrie)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0050157 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0050157 "PERSON: Markus Schilling")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050157 "3D Geometrie"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0050157 "shape 3d"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050157 "A shape 3D is a geometry shape that exists in three dimensions, having length, width, and height, and can be defined by its spatial properties such as volume and surface area."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0050157 "Eine 3D Geometrie ist eine geometrische Form, die in drei Dimensionen existiert, mit Länge, Breite und Höhe, und die durch ihre räumlichen Eigenschaften wie Volumen und Oberfläche definiert werden kann."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0050157 "Beispiele sind Formen wie Würfel, Kugeln und Pyramiden."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0050157 "Examples include shapes like cubes, spheres, and pyramids."@en)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0050157 pmdco:PMD_0050156)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080000 (acoustic quality)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080000 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080000 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'acoustic quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080000 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080000 "acoustic quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080000 "akustische Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080000 "Acoustic quality pertains to properties related to sound or the science of sound, including aspects like pitch, volume, tone, timbre, echo, absorption, or sound wave propagation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080000 "Akustische Qualität bezieht sich auf Eigenschaften, die mit Klang oder der Klangwissenschaft in Zusammenhang stehen, einschließlich Aspekten wie Tonhöhe, Lautstärke, Ton, Klangfarbe, Echo, Absorption oder Schallwellenausbreitung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080000 "The acoustic quality of a concert hall material is characterized by its absorption and reflection coefficients"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080000 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080000 pmdco:PMD_0000506)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080001 (electrical quality)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080001 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080001 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electrical quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080001 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080001 "electrical quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080001 "elektrische Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080001 "Die elektrische Qualität charakterisiert das Verhalten oder den Zustand einer materiellen Einheit in Bezug auf Elektrizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080001 "Electrical quality characterizes a material entity's behavior or state concerning electricity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080001 "The semiconductivity of silicon is an electrical quality that determines its behavior in transistors"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080001 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080001 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080002 (magnetic quality)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080002 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080002 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'magnetic quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080002 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080002 "magnetic quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080002 "magnetische Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080002 "Die magnetische Qualität charakterisiert die Reaktion eines materiellen Gebildes auf äußere Magnetfelder oder die Emission von Magnetfeldern"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080002 "Magnetic quality characterizes a material entity's response to external magnetic fields or its emission of magnetic fields"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080002 "The magnetic susceptibility of paramagnetic aluminum is a magnetic quality measured by a magnetometer"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080002 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080002 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080003 (mechanische Qualität)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080003 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080003 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'mechanical quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080003 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080003 "mechanical quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080003 "mechanische Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080003 "Die mechanische Qualität bezieht sich auf die Leistung eines Materials, wenn es mechanischen Belastungen standhält"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080003 "Mechanical quality is related to the performance of a material when enduring mechanical loads"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080003 "The fatigue strength of a connecting rod is a mechanical quality critical for engine reliability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080003 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080003 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080004 (optische Qualität)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080004 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080004 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'optical quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080004 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080004 "optical quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080004 "optische Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080004 "Die optische Qualität charakterisiert die Interaktionsergebnisse materieller Einheiten mit Lichtemissionen oder deren Erzeugung von Lichtemissionen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080004 "Optical quality characterizes the interaction results of material entities with light emissions or their generation of light emissions"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080004 "The optical quality of a mirror is assessed by its surface flatness and reflectance uniformity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080004 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080004 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080005 (thermo dynamic quality)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080005 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080005 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'thermo dynamic quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080005 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080005 "thermo dynamic quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080005 "thermodynamische Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080005 "Thermo dynamic quality characterizes a material entity's behavior or state in relation to thermal heating or cooling"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080005 "Thermodynamische Qualität beschreibt das Verhalten oder den Zustand eines materiellen Wesens in Bezug auf thermische Erwärmung oder Kühlung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080005 "The melting point of iron at 1538 C is a thermo dynamic quality governing its processing in a blast furnace"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080005 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080005 obo:BFO_0000019)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080006 (fluid dynamic quality)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080006 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080006 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'fluid dynamic quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080006 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080006 "Strömungsqualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080006 "fluid dynamic quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080006 "Qualität der Strömungslehre"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080006 "Die dynamische Fluidqualität charakterisiert das Verhalten oder den Zustand einer materiellen Einheit in Bezug auf die Fluidinteraktion"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080006 "Fluid dynamic quality characterizes a material entity's behavior or state in relation to fluidic interaction"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080006 "The Reynolds number of flow in a pipe is a fluid dynamic quality determining laminar or turbulent regime"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080006 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080006 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080007 (radiologische Qualität)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080007 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080007 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'radiologic quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080007 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080007 "radiologic quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080007 "radiologische Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080007 "Radiologic quality pertains to properties or characteristics related to an entity's interaction with radiant energy"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080007 "Radiologische Qualität bezieht sich auf die Eigenschaften oder Merkmale im Zusammenhang mit der Wechselwirkung einer Entität mit Strahlungsenergie"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080007 "The dose equivalent a patient receives from a chest X-ray is a radiologic quality of the examination"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080007 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080007 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080008 (olfactoric quality)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080008 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080008 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'olfactoric quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080008 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080008 "olfactoric quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080008 "olfaktorische Qualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080008 "Die olfaktorische Menge bezieht sich auf die qualitativen Eigenschaften einer materiellen Einheit, wie sie vom Duftsystem wahrgenommen werden"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080008 "Olfactoric quantity relates to a material entity's qualitative characteristics as perceived by the scent system"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080008 "The pungent olfactoric quality of ammonia is detectable at concentrations above 5 ppm"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080008 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080008 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080009 (volumetrische Dichte)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080009 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080009 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080009 "volumetric density"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080009 "volumetrische Dichte"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080009 "Skalare Größe, die den Betrag einer physikalischen Eigenschaft (wie Masse, Ladung oder Anzahl der Teilchen) pro Volumeneinheit einer Substanz oder eines Raumbereichs darstellt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080009 "scalar quantity representing the amount of a physical property (such as mass, charge, or number of particles) per unit volume of a substance or region of space"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080009 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080009 pmdco:PMD_0020131)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080010 (räumliche Relationsqualität)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080010 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080010 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'spatial relational quality' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'BFO_0000145'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080010 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080010 "räumliche Relationsqualität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080010 "spatial relational quality"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080010 "Räumliche Beziehungsqualität ist eine Qualität, die einer materiellen Entität aufgrund ihrer räumlichen Beziehung zu einer oder mehreren anderen Entitäten, wie z. B. Position, Ausrichtung oder Entfernung, innewohnt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080010 "Spatial relational quality is a quality that inheres in a material entity by virtue of its spatial relationship to one or more other entities, such as position, orientation, or distance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080010 "the distance between a bolt and the nearest edge of a steel plate is a spatial relational quality of the bolt"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080010 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080010 obo:BFO_0000145)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080011 (Geschwindigkeit)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080011 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080011 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'speed' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical process characteristic'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Speed."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080011 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080011 <https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Speed>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080011 "Geschwindigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080011 "speed"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080011 "Geschwindigkeit beschreibt die Entfernung, die ein Objekt in einer bestimmten Zeit zurücklegt, immer positiv"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080011 "Speed describes the distance an object moves in a given amount of time, always positive"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080011 "If a train takes 1 hour to travel 100 kilometers, it has a speed of 100 kilometers per hour (62 mph)"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080011 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080011 pmdco:PMD_0000008)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080012 (elektrischer Strom)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080012 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080012 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electric current' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical process characteristic'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080012 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080012 "electric current"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080012 "elektrischer Strom"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080012 "electric current"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080012 "Electric current is the flow of electric charge per unit time"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080012 "Elektrischer Strom ist der Fluss elektrischer Ladung pro Zeiteinheit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080012 "A 100 W incandescent bulb draws an electric current of about 0.43 A at 230 V"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080012 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080012 pmdco:PMD_0000008)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080013 (force rate)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080013 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080013 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'force rate' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical process characteristic'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080013 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080013 "Kraftrate"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080013 "force rate"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080013 "Ruck"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080013 "yank"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080013 "In der Physik wird der Begriff \"Ruck\" manchmal verwendet, um die Ableitung der Kraft in Bezug auf die Zeit oder die mit dem Ruck multiplizierte Masse zu bezeichnen. In der relativistischen Physik wird dieser Begriff als die zweite Ableitung des Impulses in Bezug auf die Zeit ausgedrückt, da die Masse geschwindigkeitsabhängig ist. Obwohl nicht allgemein als offizieller Begriff für diese Größe anerkannt, wird der Begriff \"Ruck\" häufig von Physikbegeisterten verwendet"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080013 "In physics, yank is sometimes used to denote the derivative of force with respect to time or mass multiplied by jerk. In relativistic physics, it is expressed as the second derivative of momentum with respect to time, because the mass is velocity-dependent. Though not universally accepted as an official term for this quantity, the term \"yank\" is commonly used among physics enthusiasts"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080013 "During impact testing, the force rate on the specimen rises to 10 kN/ms within the first microsecond"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080013 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080013 pmdco:PMD_0000008)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080014 (mass flow rate)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080014 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080014 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'mass flow rate' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical process characteristic'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mass_flow_rate."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080014 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080014 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mass_flow_rate>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080014 "Massendurchsatz"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080014 "mass flow rate"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080014 "Der Massendurchfluss quantifiziert die pro Zeiteinheit fließende Masse und wird üblicherweise in Kilogramm pro Sekunde oder Pfund pro Sekunde gemessen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080014 "Mass flow rate quantifies the mass passing per unit time, commonly measured in kilograms per second or pounds per second"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080014 "A coolant pump delivers a mass flow rate of 2 kg/s of water through a heat exchanger"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080014 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080014 pmdco:PMD_0000008)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080015 (mechanischer Impuls)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080015 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080015 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'mechanical impulse' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical process characteristic'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Impulse_(physics)."@en)
