AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080019 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'area' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'DimensionQuality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0001323."@en)
