AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080019 "Fläche bedeutet eine zweidimensionale Ausdehnungsqualität, die aufgrund der zweidimensionalen Ausdehnung des Trägers inhärent ist"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080019 "The cross-sectional area of a tensile specimen at the gauge section is 50 mm2"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080019 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080019 pmdco:PMD_0020132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080021 (sound reflection coefficient)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080021 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080021 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'sound reflection coefficient' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'acoustic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
