# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080022 (elektrische Ladung)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080022 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080022 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electric charge' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'electrical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080022 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080022 "electric charge"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080022 "elektrische Ladung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080022 "electric charge"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080022 "elektrische Ladung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080022 "Electric charge refers to the physical property of matter causing it to experience a force when placed in an electromagnetic field"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080022 "Elektrische Ladung bezieht sich auf die physikalische Eigenschaft von Materie, die dazu führt, dass sie eine Kraft erfährt, wenn sie in ein elektromagnetisches Feld gebracht wird"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080022 "A capacitor stores 10 µC of electric charge at a voltage of 5 V"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080022 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080022 pmdco:PMD_0080001)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080023 (elektrische Feldstärke)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080023 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080023 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electric field strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'electrical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://www.britannica.com/science/electric-field."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080023 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080023 <https://www.britannica.com/science/electric-field>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080023 "electric field strength"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080023 "elektrische Feldstärke"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080023 "Die Stärke oder Intensität des elektrischen Feldes bezieht sich auf die Stärke und Richtung des elektrischen Feldes an einem Punkt und ist entscheidend für die Bestimmung der Auswirkungen auf elektrische Ladungen in der Nähe dieses Punktes"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080023 "Electric field strength, or intensity, refers to the magnitude and direction of the electric field at a point, crucial for determining effects on electric charges near that point"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080023 "Between parallel capacitor plates separated by 1 mm at 100 V, the electric field strength is 1e5 V/m"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080023 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080023 pmdco:PMD_0080001)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080024 (dielectric strength)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080024 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080024 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'dielectric strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'electrical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080024 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080024 "Durchschlagsfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080024 "dielectric strength"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080024 "Dielektrische Festigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080024 "E_ds"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080024 "Dielectric strength is an electrical quality of an insulating material that specifies the maximum electric field intensity the material can sustain without undergoing electrical breakdown"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080024 "Durchschlagsfestigkeit ist eine elektrische Qualität eines Isoliermaterials, die die maximale elektrische Feldstärke angibt, die das Material aushalten kann, ohne einen elektrischen Durchschlag zu erleiden"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080024 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080024 pmdco:PMD_0080001)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080025 (magnetic flux)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080025 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080025 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'magnetic flux' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'magnetic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080025 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080025 "magnetic flux"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080025 "magnetischer Fluss"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080025 "Magnetfeld"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080025 "magnetic field"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080025 "magnetic flux"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080025 "magnetischer Fluss"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080025 "Magnetic flux is the total number of magnetic field lines passing through a given area"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080025 "Magnetischer Fluss ist die Gesamtanzahl der Magnetfeldlinien, die durch eine bestimmte Fläche verlaufen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080025 "A transformer core carries a magnetic flux of 1 mWb through its cross-section at rated voltage"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080025 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080025 pmdco:PMD_0080002)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080026 (magnetische Permeabilität)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080026 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080026 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'magnetic permeability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'magnetic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080026 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080026 "magnetic permeability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080026 "magnetische Permeabilität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080026 "Permeabilität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080026 "permeability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080026 "μ"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080026 "Magnetic permeability is a magnetic quality of a material that quantifies its ability to support the formation of a magnetic field within itself, expressed as the ratio of magnetic flux density to the applied magnetic field intensity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080026 "Magnetische Permeabilität ist eine magnetische Qualität eines Materials, die seine Fähigkeit quantifiziert, ein Magnetfeld in seinem Inneren zu unterstützen, ausgedrückt als Verhältnis der magnetischen Flussdichte zur aufgebrachten magnetischen Feldstärke"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080026 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080026 pmdco:PMD_0080002)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080027 (coercivity)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080027 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080027 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'coercivity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'magnetic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080027 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080027 "Koerzitivfeldstärke"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080027 "coercivity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080027 "H_c"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080027 "Koerzitivkraft"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080027 "coercive field"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080027 "coercive force"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080027 "Coercivity is a magnetic quality of a ferromagnetic material that specifies the magnitude of the applied magnetic field required to reduce its magnetization to zero after it has been fully magnetised"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080027 "Koerzitivfeldstärke ist eine magnetische Qualität eines ferromagnetischen Materials, die die Stärke des aufzubringenden Magnetfelds angibt, das erforderlich ist, um seine Magnetisierung nach vollständiger Magnetisierung auf null zu reduzieren"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080027 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080027 pmdco:PMD_0080002)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080029 (strain)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080029 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080029 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'strain' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'deformation'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strain_(mechanics)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080029 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080029 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strain_(mechanics)>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080029 "Dehnung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080029 "strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080029 "Dehnung ist als relative Verformung definiert, verglichen mit einer Referenzpositionskonfiguration"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080029 "Strain is defined as relative deformation, compared to a reference position configuration"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080029 "Under a tensile load, a polymer film exhibits a strain of 2 % before yielding"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080029 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080029 pmdco:PMD_0080003)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080030 (technische Dehnung)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080030 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080030 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'engineering strain' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strain'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strain_(mechanics)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080030 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080030 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strain_(mechanics)>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080030 "engineering strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080030 "technische Dehnung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080030 "Cauchy strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080030 "technical strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080030 "Die technische Dehnung oder Cauchy-Dehnung drückt die Gesamtverformung relativ zur ursprünglichen Abmessung des Materials unter Last aus und spiegelt die Dehnung bei axialer Belastung wider"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080030 "Engineering strain, or Cauchy strain, expresses total deformation relative to the initial dimension of the material under load, reflecting elongation in axial loading"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080030 "A tensile specimen elongates from 50 mm to 55 mm gauge length, giving an engineering strain of 10 %"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080030 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080030 pmdco:PMD_0080029)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080031 (Kriechverformung)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080031 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080031 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'creep strain' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strain'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080031 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080031 "Kriechverformung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080031 "creep strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080031 "Kriechbeanspruchung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080031 "Kriechverformung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080031 "creep strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080031 "creeping strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080031 "Creep strain occurs when a material is subjected to constant stress over a long period of time"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080031 "Eine Kriechverformung tritt auf, wenn ein Material einer konstanten Belastung über einen langen Zeitraum ausgesetzt ist"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080031 "A nickel alloy turbine blade accumulates 0.5 % creep strain after 10000 hours at 900 C"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080031 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080031 pmdco:PMD_0080029)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080032 (true strain)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080032 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080032 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'true strain' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strain'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strain_(mechanics)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080032 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080032 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strain_(mechanics)>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080032 "true strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080032 "wahre Dehnung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080032 "Hencky strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080032 "logarithmic strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080032 "True strain, or logarithmic strain, integrates incrementally over deformation; related to engineering strain as ε=ln(1+e)"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080032 "Wahre Dehnung, auch als logarithmische Dehnung bekannt, integriert sich schrittweise über die Verformung; in Beziehung zum technischen Dehnungsmaß als ε=ln(1+e)"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080032 "At a cross-section reduction of 50 %, the true strain is ln(2) = 0.693"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080032 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080032 pmdco:PMD_0080029)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080033 (Bruchdehnung)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080033 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080033 "StrainAtBreak(x) ↔ Strain(x) ∧ ∃b∃p∃i(obo:BFO_0000040(b) ∧ MeasurementProcess(p) ∧ MeasurementInformationContentEntity(i) ∧ bearerOf(b, x) ∧ describes(i, x) ∧ isOutputOf(i, p) ∧ ∃t(TimeOfBreak(t) ∧ occupiesTemporalRegion(p, t)))"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080033 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080033 "Bruchdehnung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080033 "strain at break"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080033 "elongation at break"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080033 "Bruchdehnung ist die Dehnung einer Probe im Moment des Bruchs, bestimmt unter Zugbelastung gemäß anwendbaren Prüfnormen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080033 "Strain at break is the strain of a specimen at the moment of fracture, determined under tensile load according to applicable test standards"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080033 "Strain at break of a thermoplastic polyurethane specimen measured as 450% under ISO 527 test conditions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080033 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080033 pmdco:PMD_0080029)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080034 (elastische Deformation)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080034 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080034 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'elastic strain' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strain'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plasticity_(physics)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080034 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080034 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plasticity_(physics)>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080034 "elastic strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080034 "elastische Deformation"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080034 "elastic deformation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080034 "elastische Verformung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080034 "Bei der elastischen Dehnung handelt es sich um eine Dehnungsqualität eines Materialgebildes, die durch eine reversible Verformung gekennzeichnet ist, die bei Wegnahme der aufgebrachten Last verschwindet"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080034 "Elastic strain is a strain quality of a material entity characterized by reversible deformation that disappears upon removal of the applied load"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080034 "Steel loaded to 200 MPa exhibits an elastic strain of about 0.001, fully recovered upon unloading"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080034 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080034 pmdco:PMD_0080029)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080035 (plastic strain)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080035 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080035 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'plastic strain' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strain'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plasticity_(physics)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080035 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080035 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plasticity_(physics)>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080035 "plastic strain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080035 "plastische Deformation"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080035 "plastic deformation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080035 "plastische Verformung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080035 "Plastic strain describes permanent deformation occurring when a material is subjected to stress beyond its elastic limit"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080035 "Plastische Deformation beschreibt die dauerhafte Verformung, die auftritt, wenn ein Material einer Belastung ausgesetzt wird, die über seine elastische Grenze hinausgeht"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080035 "After exceeding yield strength, a steel rod undergoes 5 % plastic strain that remains after unloading"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080035 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080035 pmdco:PMD_0080029)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080036 (luminous intensity)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080036 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080036 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'luminous intensity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'optical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080036 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080036 "Lichtstärke in cd gemessen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080036 "luminous intensity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080036 "Leuchtintensität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080036 "Lichtintensität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080036 "luminous intensity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080036 "Lichtstärke ist die Menge des sichtbaren Lichts, das pro Einheitswinkel in eine bestimmte Richtung von einer Quelle abgestrahlt wird, gemessen in Candela (cd)"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080036 "Luminous intensity quantifies the visible light emitted per unit solid angle in a particular direction from a source, measured in candela (cd)"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080036 "A standard LED lamp emits a luminous intensity of 800 cd in the forward direction"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080036 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080036 pmdco:PMD_0080004)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080037 (Belichtungszeit)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080037 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080037 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'exposure' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'optical quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exposure_(photography)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080037 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080037 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exposure_(photography)>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080037 "Belichtungszeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080037 "exposure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080037 "Exposure in photography refers to the amount of light per unit area reaching film or sensor, determined by shutter speed, lens F-number, and scene luminance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080037 "Unter Belichtung versteht man in der Fotografie die Lichtmenge pro Flächeneinheit, die den Film oder Sensor erreicht, bestimmt durch Verschlusszeit, Blendenzahl des Objektivs und Helligkeit der Szene"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080037 "A worker is exposed to a UV radiation exposure of 30 J/m2 during outdoor operations"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080037 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080037 pmdco:PMD_0080004)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080038 (Curie temperature)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080038 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080038 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'Curie temperature' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermo dynamic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080038 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080038 "Curie temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080038 "Curie-Temperatur"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080038 "Curie point"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080038 "Curie-Punkt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080038 "T_C"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080038 "Curie temperature is a thermodynamic quality of a ferromagnetic material that specifies the temperature above which it loses its permanent magnetic ordering and becomes paramagnetic"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080038 "Curie-Temperatur ist eine thermodynamische Qualität eines ferromagnetischen Materials, die die Temperatur angibt, oberhalb derer das Material seine permanente magnetische Ordnung verliert und paramagnetisch wird"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080038 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080038 pmdco:PMD_0000967)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080039 (spezifische Wärmekapazität)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080039 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080039 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'specific heat capacity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermo dynamic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080039 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080039 "specific heat capacity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080039 "spezifische Wärmekapazität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080039 "Specific heat capacity is the heat capacity of a sample divided by its mass, representing the heat required to raise temperature by one unit"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080039 "Spezifische Wärmekapazität ist die Wärmekapazität einer Probe geteilt durch ihre Masse und repräsentiert die erforderliche Wärme, um die Temperatur um eine Einheit zu erhöhen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080039 "Water has a specific heat capacity of 4182 J/(kg·K), making it an effective coolant"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080039 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080039 pmdco:PMD_0080005)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080040 (eutectic point)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080040 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080040 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'eutectic point' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermo dynamic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080040 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080040 "eutectic point"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080040 "eutektischer Punkt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080040 "eutectic temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080040 "eutektische Temperatur"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080040 "Eutectic point is a thermodynamic quality of a multi-component material system that specifies the composition and temperature at which all components simultaneously solidify from a liquid mixture at the lowest possible melting temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080040 "Eutektischer Punkt ist eine thermodynamische Qualität eines Mehrkomponentenmaterialsystems, die die Zusammensetzung und Temperatur angibt, bei der alle Komponenten gleichzeitig aus einer flüssigen Mischung bei der niedrigstmöglichen Schmelztemperatur erstarren"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080040 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080040 pmdco:PMD_0020164)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080041 (kritischer Druck)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080041 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080041 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'critical pressure' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermo dynamic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080041 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080041 "critical pressure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080041 "kritischer Druck"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080041 "p_c"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080041 "Critical pressure is a thermodynamic quality of a pure substance that specifies the minimum pressure required to liquefy the substance at its critical temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080041 "Kritischer Druck ist eine thermodynamische Qualität einer reinen Substanz, die den Mindestdruck angibt, der erforderlich ist, um die Substanz bei ihrer kritischen Temperatur zu verflüssigen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080041 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080041 pmdco:PMD_0080005)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080042 (kritische Temperatur)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080042 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080042 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'critical temperature' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermo dynamic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080042 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080042 "critical temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080042 "kritische Temperatur"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080042 "T_c"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080042 "Critical temperature is a thermodynamic quality of a pure substance that specifies the temperature above which the substance cannot exist as a liquid regardless of applied pressure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080042 "Kritische Temperatur ist eine thermodynamische Qualität einer reinen Substanz, die die Temperatur angibt, oberhalb derer die Substanz unabhängig vom aufgebrachten Druck nicht als Flüssigkeit existieren kann"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080042 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080042 pmdco:PMD_0000967)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080044 (Alterungstemperatur)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080044 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080044 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'aging temperature' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'temperature'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080044 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080044 "Alterungstemperatur"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080044 "aging temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080044 "Aging temperature refers to variable temperature during an aging process depending on the desired deposition formations"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080044 "Unter Alterungstemperatur versteht man die variable Temperatur während eines Alterungsprozesses in Abhängigkeit von der gewünschten Ablagerungsbildung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080044 "Al-Cu alloys are artificially aged at 175 C to precipitate strengthening phases"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080044 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080044 pmdco:PMD_0000967)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080045 (Umgebungstemperatur)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080045 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080045 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'environmental temperature' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'temperature'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080045 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080045 "Umgebungstemperatur"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080045 "environmental temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080045 "Environmental temperature describes the observed temperature surrounding a tangible object, including room temperature and temperatures measured in test chambers"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080045 "Umgebungstemperatur ist die Eigenschaft, die die beobachtete Temperatur in der Umgebung eines betrachteten materiellen Objekts beschreibt. Dazu gehören Raumtemperatur und die in Prüfkammern gemessenen Temperaturen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080045 "A circuit board operates at an environmental temperature of 85 C in a high-reliability application"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080045 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080045 pmdco:PMD_0000967)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080046 (Dampfdruck)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080046 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080046 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'vapor pressure' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermo dynamic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080046 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080046 "Dampfdruck"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080046 "vapor pressure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080046 "p*"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080046 "Dampfdruck ist eine thermodynamische Qualität eines Stoffes, die den Druck angibt, den sein Dampf ausübt, wenn er sich bei einer gegebenen Temperatur im thermodynamischen Gleichgewicht mit seiner kondensierten Phase befindet"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080046 "Vapor pressure is a thermodynamic quality of a substance that specifies the pressure exerted by its vapor when in thermodynamic equilibrium with its condensed phase at a given temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080046 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080046 pmdco:PMD_0080005)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080047 (flash point)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080047 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080047 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'flash point' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermo dynamic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080047 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080047 "Flammpunkt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080047 "flash point"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080047 "Flammpunkt ist eine thermodynamische Qualität eines flüchtigen Materials, die die niedrigste Temperatur angibt, bei der sein Dampf an der Materialoberfläche ein zündfähiges Gemisch mit Luft bildet"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080047 "Flash point is a thermodynamic quality of a volatile material that specifies the lowest temperature at which its vapour forms an ignitable mixture with air near the surface of the material"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080047 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080047 pmdco:PMD_0080005)

