AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080048 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'ductile-brittle transition temperature' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermo dynamic quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080048 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080048 "Duktil-Spröd-Übergangstemperatur"@de)
