AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080103 "volume concentration"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080103 "Volume concentration links the volume of a mixture component to the total volume, crucial for quantitative composition description"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080103 "Volumenkonzentration verbindet das Volumen eines Mischbestandteils mit dem Gesamtvolumen, entscheidend für die quantitative Zusammensetzungsbeschreibung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080103 "A paint pigment dispersion has a TiO2 volume concentration of 20 %"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080103 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080103 pmdco:PMD_0020104)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080104 (volume fraction)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080104 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080104 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'volume fraction' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'volume ratio'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volumenkonzentration."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080104 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080104 <https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volumenkonzentration>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080104 "Volumenanteil"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080104 "volume fraction"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080104 "Volume fraction describes the volume of a mixture component relative to the sum of all components' volumes"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080104 "Volumenanteil beschreibt das Volumen eines Mischbestandteils im Verhältnis zur Summe der Volumina aller Bestandteile"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080104 "A dual-phase steel contains a martensite volume fraction of 20 %, controlling its strength-ductility balance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080104 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080104 pmdco:PMD_0020104)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080105 (Mischengehaltverhältnis)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080105 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080105 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'volume mix ratio' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'volume ratio'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volumenverh%C3%A4ltnis."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080105 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080105 <https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volumenverh%C3%A4ltnis>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080105 "Mischengehaltverhältnis"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080105 "volume mix ratio"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080105 "Mischengehaltverhältnis definiert das Verhältnis der Volumina von zwei Mischbestandteilen zueinander"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080105 "Volume mix ratio defines the ratio of volumes of two mixture components to each other"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080105 "An epoxy adhesive is mixed in a volume mix ratio of 2:1 resin to hardener"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080105 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080105 pmdco:PMD_0020104)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080106 (piezoelectric coefficient)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080106 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080106 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'piezoelectric coefficient' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical relational quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080106 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080106 "piezoelectric coefficient"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080106 "piezoelektrischer Koeffizient"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080106 "d"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080106 "piezoelectric constant"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080106 "piezoelektrische Konstante"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080106 "Piezoelectric coefficient is a physical relational quality of a material that quantifies the coupling between mechanical stress and electric polarization, expressed as the ratio of electric displacement to applied mechanical stress or the ratio of strain to applied electric field"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080106 "Piezoelektrischer Koeffizient ist eine physikalische relationale Qualität eines Materials, die die Kopplung zwischen mechanischer Spannung und elektrischer Polarisation quantifiziert, ausgedrückt als Verhältnis der elektrischen Verschiebung zur angelegten mechanischen Spannung oder des Dehnungsanteils zum angelegten elektrischen Feld"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080106 "The d33 piezoelectric coefficient of PZT ceramics is about 400 pC/N, enabling sensitive force sensing"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080106 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080106 pmdco:PMD_0080069)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080107 (Klemmdruck)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080107 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080107 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'clamping pressure' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'pressure'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080107 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080107 "Klemmdruck"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080107 "clamping pressure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080107 "Clamping pressure describes the force per area used during the mounting process of a sample, typically involving grips or similar tools"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080107 "Klemmdruck ist die Eigenschaft, die als quantitativer Wert die Kraft pro Fläche beschreibt, die beim Einbau einer Probe, eines Prüfkörpers oder eines Prüfstücks aufgebracht wird, typischerweise verbunden mit einer Art von Klemm- oder Spannzubehör"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080107 "A hydraulic fixture applies a clamping pressure of 5 MPa to hold a workpiece during machining"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080107 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080107 pmdco:PMD_0000896)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080108 (Spannung)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080108 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080108 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'stress' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'pressure'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080108 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080108 "Spannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080108 "stress"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080108 "Spannung ist die innere Kraft pro Flächeneinheit, die ein Material unter äußerer Belastung erfährt, und wird häufig als Zug-, Druck- oder Scherspannung beschrieben"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080108 "Stress is the internal force per unit area a material experiences under external load, commonly described in tensile, compressive, or shear forms"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080108 "A cross-section of a loaded steel column bears a compressive stress of 150 MPa"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080108 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080108 pmdco:PMD_0000896)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080109 (engineering stress)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080109 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080109 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'engineering stress' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'stress'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080109 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080109 "engineering stress"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080109 "technische Spannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080109 "Engineering stress quantifies the internal force per unit area a material experiences under load, assuming the area remains constant"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080109 "Technische Spannung beschreibt die innere Kraft pro Fläche, die ein Material unter Last erfährt, unter der Annahme, dass die Fläche konstant bleibt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080109 "At yield, a steel specimen with 50 mm2 cross-section under 12.5 kN shows engineering stress of 250 MPa"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080109 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080109 pmdco:PMD_0080108)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080110 (true stress)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080110 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080110 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'true stress' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'stress'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080110 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080110 "true stress"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080110 "wahre Spannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080110 "True stress is defined using the cauchy stress tensor, relating stress to the current surface size of a volume element"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080110 "Wahre Spannung wird unter Verwendung des Cauchy-Spannungstensors definiert und bezieht die Spannung auf die aktuelle Oberflächengröße eines Volumenelements"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080110 "At 10 % engineering strain in a tensile test, the true stress exceeds the engineering stress by the same factor"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080110 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080110 pmdco:PMD_0080108)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080111 (creep stress)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080111 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080111 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'creep stress' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'stress'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080111 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080111 "Kriechspannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080111 "creep stress"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080111 "Creep stress is characterized by strain occurring with time when a constant force is applied to a physical body"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080111 "Unter Kriechspannung versteht man eine Belastung, die mit der Zeit auftritt, wenn eine konstante Kraft auf einen physischen Körper ausgeübt wird"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080111 "A polymer gasket under a creep stress of 5 MPa at 60 C relaxes significantly over 1000 hours"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080111 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080111 pmdco:PMD_0080108)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080112 (Adhäsion)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080112 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080112 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'adhesion' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'pressure'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080112 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080112 "Adhäsion"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080112 "adhesion"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080112 "Adhesion describes the ability of substances to bind to each other, involving attractive force between two bodies of different substances in contact and influencing material performance in scientific and industrial contexts"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080112 "Adhäsion beschreibt die Fähigkeit von Substanzen, sich aneinander zu binden. Dabei handelt es sich um eine Anziehungskraft zwischen zwei in Kontakt stehenden Körpern unterschiedlicher Substanzen, die die Materialleistung in wissenschaftlichen und industriellen Kontexten beeinflusst"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080112 "The adhesion between a paint film and a steel substrate determines its resistance to delamination"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080112 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080112 pmdco:PMD_0000896)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080113 (surface tension)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080113 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080113 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'surface tension' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'adhesion'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080113 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080113 "Oberflächenspannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080113 "surface tension"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080113 "Oberflächenspannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080113 "surface stress"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080113 "surface tension"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080113 "Oberflächenspannung bezeichnet den Effekt innerhalb der Oberflächenschicht einer Flüssigkeit, der durch Wechselwirkungskräfte zwischen ihren Molekülen verursacht wird"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080113 "Surface tension refers to the effect within the surface layer of a liquid, caused by intermolecular forces between its molecules"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080113 "Water has a surface tension of 72.8 mN/m at 20 C, enabling capillary rise in fine tubes"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080113 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080113 pmdco:PMD_0080112)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080114 (refractive index)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080114 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080114 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'refractive index' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical relational quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Refractive_index#Complex_index_of_refraction_and_absorption."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080114 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080114 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Refractive_index#Complex_index_of_refraction_and_absorption>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080114 "Brechzahl"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080114 "refractive index"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080114 "Brechzahl gibt die Lichtbrechungsfähigkeit eines optischen Mediums an; umfasst einen realen und einen imaginären Teil, der als Extinktionskoeffizient bekannt ist"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080114 "Refractive index indicates an optical medium's light bending ability; encompassing a real and imaginary part known as the extinction coefficient"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080114 "Optical glass BK7 has a refractive index of 1.52 at 589 nm, bending light in lenses"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080114 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080114 pmdco:PMD_0080069)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080115 (Extinktionskoeffizient)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080115 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080115 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'extinction coefficient' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'refractive index'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Refractive_index#Complex_index_of_refraction_and_absorption."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080115 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080115 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Refractive_index#Complex_index_of_refraction_and_absorption>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080115 "Extinktionskoeffizient"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080115 "extinction coefficient"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080115 "Der Extinktionskoeffizient, die imaginäre Komponente des komplexen Brechungsindex, gibt die Dämpfung elektromagnetischer Wellen durch ein Material an"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080115 "Extinction coefficient, the imaginary component of the complex refractive index, indicates attenuation of electromagnetic waves through a material"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080115 "The extinction coefficient of gold at 500 nm wavelength is 1.87, characterizing strong optical absorption"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080115 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080115 pmdco:PMD_0080114)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080116 (potential)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080116 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080116 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'potential' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical relational quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080116 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080116 "Potenzial"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080116 "potential"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080116 "Potential describes the capacity of an entity to perform work or transform due to its position or configuration within a system"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080116 "Potenzial beschreibt die Fähigkeit einer Entität, Arbeit zu leisten oder sich aufgrund ihrer Position oder Konfiguration innerhalb eines Systems zu transformieren"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080116 "The gravitational potential at the top of a 10 m column of water corresponds to a pressure head of 98 kPa"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080116 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080116 pmdco:PMD_0080069)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080118 (Massenpotential)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080118 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080118 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'mass potential' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'potential'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080118 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080118 "Massenpotential"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080118 "mass potential"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080118 "Das Massenpotential definiert eine skalare Größe, die die aufgrund der Position, Form oder Konfiguration eines Materials gespeicherte Energie beschreibt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080118 "Mass potential defines a scalar quantity describing energy stored due to a material's position, shape, or configuration"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080118 "The mass potential of a raised water reservoir drives flow through a turbine at lower elevation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080118 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080118 pmdco:PMD_0080116)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080119 (Wärmeübergangskoeffizient)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080119 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080119 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'heat transfer coefficient' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical relational quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heat_transfer_coefficient."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080119 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080119 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heat_transfer_coefficient>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080119 "Wärmeübergangskoeffizient"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080119 "heat transfer coefficient"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080119 "Der Wärmeübertragungskoeffizient stellt die Proportionalitätskonstante zwischen dem Wärmefluss und der thermodynamischen Antriebskraft für den Wärmefluss dar und wird zur Berechnung der Wärmeübertragung, typischerweise durch Konvektion, verwendet"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080119 "Heat transfer coefficient represents the proportionality constant between heat flux and the thermodynamic driving force for heat flow, used in calculating heat transfer, typically by convection"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080119 "A forced convection air-cooled heat sink has a heat transfer coefficient of 100 W/(m2·K)"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080119 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080119 pmdco:PMD_0020269)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080120 (magnetic susceptibility)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080120 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080120 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'magnetic susceptibility' have not yet been formalized. Although χ = M/H is a well-defined ratio, a formal equivalence axiom would incorrectly classify any dimensionless relational quality of a magnetic bearer as magnetic susceptibility. Defined as a primitive subtype of 'physical relational quality'."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080120 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080120 "magnetic susceptibility"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080120 "magnetische Suszeptibilität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080120 "χ"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080120 "Magnetic susceptibility is a physical relational quality of a material that quantifies the degree to which it becomes magnetized in response to an applied magnetic field, expressed as the dimensionless ratio of magnetization to applied field intensity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080120 "Magnetische Suszeptibilität ist eine physikalische relationale Qualität eines Materials, die den Grad angibt, in dem es sich als Reaktion auf ein angelegtes Magnetfeld magnetisiert, ausgedrückt als dimensionsloses Verhältnis der Magnetisierung zur angelegten Feldstärke"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080120 "Paramagnetic oxygen gas has a positive magnetic susceptibility of 3.73e-6 m3/mol at 20 C"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080120 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080120 pmdco:PMD_0020275)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080121 (Fluiddurchlässigkeit)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080121 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080121 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'fluid permeability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical relational quality'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080121 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080121 "Fluiddurchlässigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080121 "fluid permeability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080121 "Darcy permeability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080121 "Durchlässigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080121 "hydraulic permeability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080121 "k"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080121 "Fluid permeability is a physical relational quality of a porous material that quantifies its capacity to allow fluid flow through its pore network under an applied pressure gradient, defined by Darcy's law as the ratio of fluid flux to the pressure gradient normalized by fluid viscosity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080121 "Fluiddurchlässigkeit ist eine physikalische relationale Qualität eines porösen Materials, die seine Fähigkeit quantifiziert, Fluidfluss durch sein Porennetzwerk unter einem angelegten Druckgradienten zu ermöglichen, definiert durch das Darcy-Gesetz als Verhältnis des Fluidflusses zum Druckgradienten normiert durch die Viskosität des Fluids"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080121 "Sandstone with a Darcy permeability of 100 mD allows significant fluid flow under pressure gradients"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080121 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080121 pmdco:PMD_0080069)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080122 (phase velocity)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080122 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080122 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'phase velocity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'speed'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080122 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080122 "Phasengeschwindigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080122 "phase velocity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080122 "Die Phasengeschwindigkeit bezieht sich auf die Geschwindigkeit, mit der sich die Phase einer Welle ausbreitet, definiert als Wellenlänge geteilt durch die Zeitperiode"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080122 "Phase velocity refers to the rate at which the phase of a wave propagates, defined as wavelength divided by time period"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080122 "The phase velocity of a longitudinal ultrasonic wave in steel is approximately 5900 m/s"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080122 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080122 pmdco:PMD_0080011)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080123 (Deformationsgeschwindigkeit)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080123 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080123 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'deformation speed' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'speed'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strain_rate."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080123 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080123 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strain_rate>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080123 "Deformationsgeschwindigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080123 "deformation speed"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080123 "Dehnrate"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080123 "strain rate"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080123 "Deformation speed measures the rate at which distances of adjacent material parcels change with time near a specific point, including expansion and shear rates"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080123 "Die Verformungsgeschwindigkeit misst die Geschwindigkeit, mit der sich die Abstände benachbarter Materialpakete in der Nähe eines bestimmten Punktes im Laufe der Zeit ändern, einschließlich Expansions- und Schergeschwindigkeiten"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080123 "During high-rate forming, the deformation speed of the punch reaches 10 m/s"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080123 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080123 pmdco:PMD_0080011)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080125 (sound insulation index)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080125 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080125 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'sound insulation index' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'acoustic capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080125 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080125 "Schalldämmmaß"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080125 "sound insulation index"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080125 "Schalldämmmaß quantifiziert die Fähigkeit eines Materials, die Schallübertragung zu reduzieren"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080125 "Sound insulation index quantifies the ability of a material to reduce sound transmission"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080125 "A 200 mm concrete wall achieves a sound insulation index of 52 dB, blocking most airborne noise"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080125 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080125 pmdco:PMD_0000506)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080127 (elektrische Kapazität)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080127 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080127 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electrical capacitance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'electrical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080127 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080127 "electrical capacitance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080127 "elektrische Kapazität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080127 "electrical capacitance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080127 "electrical capacity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080127 "elektrische Kapazität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080127 "Die elektrische Kapazität bezieht sich auf die Fähigkeit eines Wesens, elektrische Ladung zu speichern, ausgedrückt als die Menge an elektrischer Ladung, die pro gegebenem elektrischem Potenzial gespeichert wird"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080127 "Electrical capacitance refers to an entity's ability to store electric charge, expressed as the amount of electric charge stored per given electric potential"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080127 "A ceramic capacitor has an electrical capacitance of 100 nF, storing charge in an electronic circuit"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080127 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080127 pmdco:PMD_0000621)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080128 (electrical resistance)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080128 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080128 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electrical resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'electrical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://www.britannica.com/technology/resistance-electronics."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080128 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080128 <https://www.britannica.com/technology/resistance-electronics>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080128 "electrical resistance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080128 "elektrischer Widerstand"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080128 "Der elektrische Widerstand bezieht sich auf die Fähigkeit eines Stromkreises, elektrische Energie in Wärmeenergie umzuwandeln, indem er elektrischem Strom durch Teilchenkollisionen entgegenwirkt, die für Widerstände, Lampen und Drähte charakteristisch sind"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080128 "Electrical resistance pertains to a circuit's capability to transform electric energy into heat energy, opposing electric current through particle collisions, characteristic of resistors, lamps, and wires"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080128 "A nichrome heating element has an electrical resistance of 10 Ω at room temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080128 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080128 pmdco:PMD_0000621)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080129 (electrical conductance)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080129 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080129 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electrical conductance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'electrical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080129 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080129 "electrical conductance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080129 "elektrischer Leitwert"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080129 "Stromleitwert"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080129 "electrical conductance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080129 "elektrischer Leitwert"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080129 "Der elektrische Leitwert stellt den Kehrwert des elektrischen Widerstands eines Leiters dar und misst seine Fähigkeit, elektrischen Strom zu leiten, angegeben in Siemens (S)."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080129 "Electrical conductance represents the reciprocal of a conductor's electrical resistance, measuring its ability to conduct an electric current, denoted in siemens (S)"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080129 "A copper wire of 1 m length and 1 mm2 cross-section has an electrical conductance of about 59 S"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080129 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080129 pmdco:PMD_0000621)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080130 (magnetische Fähigkeit)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080130 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080130 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'magnetic capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080130 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080130 "magnetic capability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080130 "magnetische Fähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080130 "Magnetic capability is a physical capability of a material that can be realized through interactions involving magnetic fields or magnetic ordering"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080130 "Magnetische Fähigkeit ist eine physische Fähigkeit eines Materials, die durch Wechselwirkungen mit Magnetfeldern oder magnetischer Ordnung realisiert werden kann"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080130 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080130 obo:BFO_0000016)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080131 (Sättigungsmagnetisierung)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080131 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080131 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'saturation magnetization' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'magnetic capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080131 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080131 "Sättigungsmagnetisierung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080131 "saturation magnetization"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080131 "M_s"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080131 "magnetic saturation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080131 "magnetische Sättigung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080131 "Saturation magnetization is a magnetic capability of a material that specifies the maximum magnetic moment per unit volume achieved when all magnetic domains are aligned with an applied external field"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080131 "Sättigungsmagnetisierung ist eine magnetische Fähigkeit eines Materials, die das maximale magnetische Moment pro Volumeneinheit angibt, das erreicht wird, wenn alle magnetischen Domänen mit einem angelegten äußeren Feld ausgerichtet sind"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080131 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080131 pmdco:PMD_0080130)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080133 (durability)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080133 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'durability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080133 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Dauerhaftigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080133 "durability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Dauerhaftigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Langlebigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080133 "durability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080133 "longevity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Die Dauerhaftigkeit ist die Fähigkeit eines Materials, Abnutzung, Rissbildung und andere Arten von Schäden im Laufe der Zeit zu widerstehen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Durability is the ability of a material to resist wear, tear, and other types of damage over time"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Galvanized steel shows high durability in outdoor environments, resisting corrosion for over 50 years"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080133 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080133 pmdco:PMD_0000848)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080134 (Verschleißfestigkeit)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080134 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'wear resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'durability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080134 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Verschleißfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080134 "wear resistance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Verschleißfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080134 "resistance to wear"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080134 "wear resistance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080134 "widerstand gegen Verschleiß"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Verschleißfestigkeit ist die Fähigkeit eines Materials, mechanischen Aktionen wie Reiben, Kratzen oder Erosion zu widerstehen, die dazu tendieren, Material allmählich von seiner Oberfläche zu entfernen."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Wear resistance is the ability of a material to resist mechanical actions such as rubbing, scraping or erosion that tend to progressively remove material from its surface."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Hardened tool steel has high wear resistance, maintaining a cutting edge through thousands of machining cycles"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080134 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080134 pmdco:PMD_0080133)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080135 (Kriechfestigkeit)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080135 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'creep resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'durability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080135 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Kriechfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080135 "creep resistance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Creep Resistance"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Creep Resistant"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Kriechfestig"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Kriechfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Creep resistance is the ability of a material to resist deformation under load over time"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Die Kriechfestigkeit ist die Fähigkeit eines Materials, unter Last über einen bestimmten Zeitraum eine Deformation zu widerstehen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Nickel superalloys have high creep resistance, maintaining shape under stress at 1000 C in turbine blades"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080135 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080135 pmdco:PMD_0080133)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080136 (poisson effect)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080136 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'poisson effect' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson%27s_ratio."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Was a subclass of 'Mechanical Quality'")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080136 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson%27s_ratio>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Querkontraktion"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080136 "poisson effect"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Poisson effect describes deformation perpendicular to the direction of loading, named after Siméon Poisson"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Querkontraktion beschreibt die Deformation senkrecht zur Belastungsrichtung, benannt nach Siméon Poisson"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080136 "A rubber cylinder loaded axially expands radially due to the Poisson effect, with a ratio of about 0.5"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080136 pmdco:PMD_0000848)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080137 (Poissonzahl)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080137 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'poisson's ratio' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'poisson effect'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson%27s_ratio."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080137 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080137 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson%27s_ratio>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Poissonzahl"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080137 "poisson's ratio"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Poisson's ratio is a measure of the Poisson effect, with values typically between 0.0 and 0.5 for most materials"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Poissonzahl ist ein Maß für den Poisson-Effekt, mit Werten typischerweise zwischen 0,0 und 0,5 für die meisten Materialien"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Rubber has a Poisson's ratio close to 0.5, indicating nearly incompressible behavior under loading"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080137 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080137 pmdco:PMD_0080136)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080138 (material fatigue)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080138 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'aterial fatigue' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080138 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Materialermüdung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080138 "material fatigue"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Ermüdung des Materials"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Materialermüdung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080138 "fatigue of material"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080138 "material fatigue"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Material fatigue is the failure of a material caused by repeated or sustained loading below its ultimate strength."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Materialermüdung ist das Versagen von Werkstoffen infolge wiederholter oder dauernder Belastung unterhalb der Probenfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Repeated cyclic loading at 400 MPa induces material fatigue in a steel shaft, leading to crack initiation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080138 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080138 pmdco:PMD_0000848)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080139 (Schlagenergie)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080139 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'impact energy' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080139 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Schlagenergie"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080139 "impact energy"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Charpy impact energy"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080139 "KV"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Kerbschlagenergie"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Impact energy is a mechanical capability of a material that characterises the total energy absorbed by a standardised notched specimen during fracture under a single impact blow, as measured in a Charpy or Izod test"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Schlagenergie ist eine mechanische Fähigkeit eines Materials, die die gesamte Energie beschreibt, die eine standardisierte gekerbte Probe beim Bruch unter einem einzigen Schlagimpuls absorbiert, gemessen im Charpy- oder Izod-Versuch"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080139 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080139 pmdco:PMD_0000848)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080143 (viscoelastic property)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080143 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'viscoelasticity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080143 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viscoelastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080143 "viscoelastic property"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viscoelastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viskoelastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080143 "elasticity of viscosity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080143 "viscoelasticity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viscoelasticity describes materials exhibiting both viscous and elastic characteristics during deformation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viscoelastizität beschreibt Materialien, die sowohl viskose als auch elastische Eigenschaften während der Verformung zeigen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Polymers exhibit viscoelasticity, showing both elastic recovery and creep under constant load"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080143 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080143 pmdco:PMD_0000848)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080144 (Kriechmodul)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080144 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'creep modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscoelasticity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080144 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Kriechmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080144 "creep modulus"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Kriechmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080144 "creep modulus"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Creep modulus measures a material's viscoelasticity, indicating its ability to deform under stress over time"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Der Kriechmodul ist ein Maß für die Viskoelastizität eines Materials, das seine Fähigkeit zur Verformung unter Belastung im Laufe der Zeit beschreibt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080144 "The creep modulus of polyethylene at 50 C and 1 MPa after 1000 hours is 200 MPa"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080144 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080144 pmdco:PMD_0080143)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080145 (Komplexmodul)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080145 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080145 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'complex modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscoelasticity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080145 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080145 "Komplexmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080145 "complex modulus"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080145 "E*"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080145 "Complex modulus is a viscoelastic quality of a material that represents the total stiffness response under oscillatory loading as a complex number, comprising the storage modulus as the real part and the loss modulus as the imaginary part"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080145 "Komplexmodul ist eine viskoelastische Qualität eines Materials, die die gesamte Steifigkeitsantwort unter schwingender Belastung als komplexe Zahl darstellt, bestehend aus dem Speichermodul als Realteil und dem Verlustmodul als Imaginärteil"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080145 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080145 pmdco:PMD_0080143)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080146 (Verlustmodul)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080146 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080146 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'loss modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'complex modulus'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080146 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080146 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080146 "Verlustmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080146 "loss modulus"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080146 "E''"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080146 "Loss modulus is the imaginary part of the complex modulus that measures the viscous portion of energy dissipated as heat per cycle in a viscoelastic material under oscillatory loading"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080146 "Verlustmodul ist der Imaginärteil des Komplexmoduls und misst den viskosen Anteil der pro Zyklus als Wärme dissipierten Energie in einem viskoelastischen Material unter schwingender Belastung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080146 "The loss modulus of a viscoelastic polymer at 1 Hz is 0.3 MPa, representing energy dissipation per cycle"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080146 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080146 pmdco:PMD_0080143)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080147 (dynamic modulus)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080147 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080147 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'dynamic modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'complex modulus'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080147 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080147 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080147 "dynamic modulus"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080147 "dynamischer Modul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080147 "complex shear modulus"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080147 "Dynamic modulus is the ratio of stress to strain under vibratory conditions, typically measured in shear, compression, or elongation tests, and characterizes viscoelastic materials"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080147 "Dynamischer Modul ist das Verhältnis von Spannung zu Dehnung unter schwingenden Bedingungen, typischerweise gemessen in Scher-, Druck- oder Dehnungstests, und charakterisiert viskoelastische Materialien"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080147 "The dynamic modulus of a rubber compound at 10 Hz is 15 MPa, relevant for vibration isolation design"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080147 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080147 pmdco:PMD_0080143)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080148 (Verlustwinkel)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080148 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080148 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'loss tangent' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'dynamic modulus'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080148 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080148 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080148 "Verlustwinkel"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080148 "loss tangent"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080148 "Der Verlustfaktor, dargestellt als tan δ, ist das Verhältnis des Verlustmoduls zum Speichermodul in viskoelastischen Materialien und liefert ein Maß für die Dämpfung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080148 "Loss tangent, represented as tan δ, is the ratio of the loss modulus to storage modulus in viscoelastic materials, providing a measure of damping"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080148 "A PTFE cable insulator has a loss tangent of 0.0002 at 1 GHz, minimizing signal attenuation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080148 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080148 pmdco:PMD_0080143)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080149 (Speichermodul)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080149 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080149 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'storage modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'complex modulus'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080149 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080149 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080149 "Speichermodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080149 "storage modulus"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080149 "E'"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080149 "Speichermodul ist der Realteil des Komplexmoduls und misst den elastischen Anteil der gespeicherten und zurückgewonnenen Energie pro Zyklus in einem viskoelastischen Material unter schwingender Belastung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080149 "Storage modulus is the real part of the complex modulus that measures the elastic portion of energy stored and recovered per cycle in a viscoelastic material under oscillatory loading"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080149 "The storage modulus of a polyurethane foam at 1 Hz and 25 C is 0.5 MPa, reflecting its elastic stiffness"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080149 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080149 pmdco:PMD_0080143)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080150 (Zähigkeit)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080150 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'toughness' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080150 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Zähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080150 "toughness"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Zähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080150 "toughness"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Toughness describes the resistance of a material to fracture or crack propagation, determined by its ability to absorb mechanical energy during deformation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Zähigkeit beschreibt die Widerstandsfähigkeit eines Werkstoffs gegen Bruch oder Rissausbreitung, bestimmt durch die Fähigkeit zur Absorption von mechanischer Energie bei Verformung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080150 "High-toughness tool steel absorbs 80 J before fracture in a Charpy V-notch test at room temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080150 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080150 pmdco:PMD_0000848)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080151 (fracture toughness)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080151 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'fracture toughness' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'toughness'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080151 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Bruchzähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080151 "fracture toughness"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080151 "K_Ic"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080151 "critical stress intensity factor"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Bruchzähigkeit ist eine Zähigkeitsqualität eines Materials, die die kritische Spannungsintensität beschreibt, bei der ein vorhandener Riss zu wachsen beginnt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Fracture toughness is a toughness quality of a material that specifies the critical stress intensity at which a pre-existing crack begins to propagate, expressed as the stress intensity factor at the onset of fracture"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Fracture toughness of a high-strength steel measured as 50 MPa·√m according to ISO 17281 test conditions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080151 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080151 pmdco:PMD_0080150)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080152 (impact strength)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080152 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'impact strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'toughness'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080152 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Schlagzähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080152 "impact strength"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Schlagfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Schlagzähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080152 "impact strength"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080152 "mpact strength"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Impact strength is the ability of a material to absorb energy and plastically deform without fracturing under dynamic load"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Schlagzähigkeit bezeichnet die Fähigkeit eines Materials, Energie zu absorbieren und bei Anwendung einer dynamischen Last plastisch zu verformen, ohne dass es bricht"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080152 "A Charpy impact test on notched steel gives an impact strength of 120 J, indicating good toughness"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080152 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080152 pmdco:PMD_0080150)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080153 (Bruchfestigkeit)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080153 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080153 "BreakingStrength(x) ↔ Toughness(x) ∧ ∃b∃p∃i(obo:BFO_0000040(b) ∧ MeasurementProcess(p) ∧ MeasurementInformationContentEntity(i) ∧ bearerOf(b, x) ∧ describes(i, x) ∧ isOutputOf(i, p) ∧ ∃t(TimeOfBreak(t) ∧ occupiesTemporalRegion(p, t)))"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080153 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080153 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fracture>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080153 "Bruchfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080153 "breaking strength"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080153 "Bruchspannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080153 "fracture stress"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080153 "strength at break"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080153 "stress at break"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080153 "Breaking strength is a toughness quality of a specimen that denotes the stress at which the specimen fails via fracture, recorded as the final point on a stress-strain curve"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080153 "Die Bruchfestigkeit ist eine Zähigkeitsqualität einer Probe, die die Spannung angibt, bei der die Probe durch Bruch versagt, aufgezeichnet als Endpunkt auf einer Spannungs-Dehnungs-Kurve"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080153 "A carbon fiber tow fractures at a breaking strength of 4900 MPa in a tensile test"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080153 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080153 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080154 (tensile strength)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080154 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'tensile strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'breaking strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080154 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Zugfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080154 "tensile strength"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Zugfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080154 "ultimate tensile strength"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Tensile strength measures the maximum stress a material can withstand while being stretched or pulled before breaking"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Zugfestigkeit misst die maximale Spannung, die ein Material aushalten kann, während es gestreckt oder gezogen wird, bevor es bricht"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080154 "A high-strength bolt grade 10.9 has a tensile strength of at least 1040 MPa"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080154 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080154 pmdco:PMD_0080153)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080155 (compressive strength)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080155 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080155 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'compressive strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'breaking strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
