# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080157 (shear strength)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080157 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080157 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'shear strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'breaking strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
