AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080173 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'upper yield strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'yield strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yield_(engineering)."@en)
