AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080173 "Obere Streckgrenze charakterisiert die maximale Spannung, die vor dem plastischen Fließen eines Materials angewendet werden kann"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0080173 "Upper yield strength characterizes the maximum stress that can be applied before a material begins to yield plastically"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080173 "Mild steel exhibits an upper yield strength of about 300 MPa, followed by a yield drop to the lower yield point"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080173 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
