AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080174 "Honey at 25 C has a viscosity of about 10 Pa·s, flowing slowly under gravity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080174 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080174 pmdco:PMD_0000848)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080175 (extentional viscosity)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 pmdco:PMD_0080175 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080175 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'extentional viscosity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscosity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
