AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080189 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'radiation transmission capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'optical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 pmdco:PMD_0080189 "PERSON: Thomas Hanke")
