# Individual: pmdco:PMD_0020006 (Triklines Primitiv des Bravais-Gitters)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0020006 "Triklines Primitiv des Bravais-Gitters"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0020006 "bravais lattice triclinic primitive"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0020006 "triclinic Bravais lattice with primitive centering (aP), having no rotational symmetry and all three unit cell axes of unequal length meeting at oblique angles"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition pmdco:PMD_0020006 "triklines Bravais-Gitter mit primitiver Zentrierung (aP), keine Rotationssymmetrie und alle drei Elementarzellenachsen ungleicher Länge treffen sich in schrägen Winkeln"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0020006 "true"^^xsd:boolean)

# Individual: pmdco:PMD_0020007 (monoklines Grundelement des Bravais-Gitters)

